    other_media_types multilineText [note: 'business desc: Optional field where the client can specify any additional media types not covered in the standard media placement options. Enables flexibility for unconventional requests and ensures the campaign brief captures all relevant execution preferences., technical desc: Type: multilineText, field ID: fldsBfu8Hbe84JyTS, readonly field: false']
